🔁 6. Replication Commands (DR Level)
*****Note:******* Before replication always remember on the minio dr there should be no single bucket. The minio dr should be completely empty
- Check replication status
	- mc admin replicate info dc
	eg.mc admin replicate info dc
- Add site replication
	- mc admin replicate add dc dr
	eg. mc admin replicate add dc dr
- Remove replication
	- mc admin replicate rm dc dr

📊 7. Monitoring & Health
- Cluster info
	mc admin info dc
- Disk usage
	mc admin info dc | grep drive
-  Heal (VERY IMPORTANT)
	mc admin heal dc
	👉 Used when:
		Disk failure
		Corruption
		Node recovery

🚨 8. Debugging & Logs
- Logs	
	mc admin logs dc
	
